        "type": {
          "value": "windslab",
          "display": "Wind slab"
        },
        "comment": "<p>Moderate- strong southerly and westerly winds have created fresh wind slabs in alpine and open treeline terrain as the significant amounts of recent snow are redistributed. Lake Louise had small soft slabs that propagated well up to sz 1.5. SSV reported several sz 1s that ran far but started slow.</p>",
